"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"TagComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tags"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") ,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") , sizes (from "},{"code":"AllSizesSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and borders (from "},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetagcomponenttokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"i